extends baseEmail

block content
  p Hello #{ngoName},
  p Congratulations! You have been assigned a new project by donor #{donorName}.
  p
    strong Project Details:
  ul
    li
      strong Title: 
      | #{projectTitle}
    li
      strong Description: 
      | #{projectDescription}
    li
      strong Budget: 
      | #{budget} NGN
    li
      strong Location: 
      | #{state}, #{city}
    li
      strong Donor: 
      | #{donorName}
  p This is an exciting opportunity to make a real impact in your community. Your expertise and dedication have been recognized by the donor, and we trust you'll deliver excellent results.
  p
    strong Next Steps:
  ol
    li Log in to your GivingBack dashboard
    li Review the project details and requirements
    li Submit your project implementation plan if required
    li Begin project execution according to the agreed timeline
  p You'll be able to track milestones, update progress, and communicate directly with the donor through your dashboard.
  p If you have any questions about the project or need support, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team at support@givingback.org.
  p We believe in your ability to make a meaningful difference. Let's create positive change together!
  p Thank you for your commitment to our mission.
